      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable car that still looks and feels fantastic on the road. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure! If you\u2019re looking for a solid vehicle that won't let you down, this is the one. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
