    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 sports coupe that perfectly balances daily usability with exhilarating performance. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats show only light bolstering wear, and all electronic features\u2014including the navigation and premium sound system\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been treated with the utmost respect. It comes with a complete service history, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, oil service, and brake fluid flush. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the engine pulls strongly and smoothly through every gear. This is a non-smoker vehicle that has been garaged throughout my ownership. It represents a fantastic opportunity for an enthusiast looking for a reliable, turn-key performance car that looks as good as it drives.",
      "price": 34500.0,
